OL,3,CGerard Depardieu to face criminal
OL,4,Ctrial over alleged sexual assaults on
OL,5,Cfilm set
OL,7,FFrench actor Gerard Depardieu will
OL,8,Fface criminal trial in October over
OL,9,Falleged sexual assaults on a film set,
OL,10,Fprosecutors say.
OL,12,FThe 75-year-old actor was summoned on
OL,13,FMonday morning by Paris police and
OL,14,Fplaced in custody and was questioned
OL,15,Ffor several hours.
OL,17,FThe Paris public prosecutor's office
OL,18,Fsaid in a statement that the actor has
OL,19,Fbeen "summoned to appear before the
OL,20,Fcriminal court" after the questioning.
