OL,7,FA trial will start in October "for
OL,8,Fsexual assaults likely to have been
OL,9,Fcommitted in September 2021" against
OL,10,F"two victims, on the set of the film
OL,11,F'The Green Shutters,' " the statement
OL,12,Fsaid. It did not name the alleged
OL,13,Fvictims.
OL,15,FDepardieu has denied wrongdoing. In an
OL,16,Fopen letter last October, he said: "I
OL,17,Fhave never, ever abused a woman."
