OL,7,FBFMTV and Le Parisien reported that
OL,8,Fthe police summons relates to
OL,9,Faccusations of sexual assault filed by
OL,10,Ftwo women who accuse him of groping
OL,11,Fduring filming ` one in 2014, the
OL,12,Fother in 2021.
OL,14,FThe alleged 2014 assault was reported
OL,15,Fto police in January this year, Le
OL,16,FParisien reported.
OL,18,FThe other alleged assault involved a
OL,19,F53-year-old movie decorator.
