OL,7,FDepardieu has also been accused by
OL,8,Fmore than a dozen other women of
OL,9,Fharassing, groping or sexually
OL,10,Fassaulting them.
OL,12,FHe was handed preliminary rape and
OL,13,Fsexual assault charges in 2020
OL,14,Ffollowing allegations from actor
OL,15,FCharlotte Arnould.
OL,17,FDepardieu was long seen as a national
OL,18,Ficon in France. He has been a global
OL,19,Fambassador for French film and enjoyed
OL,20,Finternational fame with several roles
OL,21,Fin Hollywood.
